WEBVTT

00:00:19.926 --> 00:00:23.904
=His Chosen Favor=

00:00:24.318 --> 00:00:26.592
(Seven Lu Zhen'ers)

00:00:27.241 --> 00:00:29.600
=Episode 16=

00:00:30.656 --> 00:00:31.536
Let go of me!

00:00:32.096 --> 00:00:32.896
Hit me again,

00:00:32.896 --> 00:00:34.432
and I'll kiss you before Xiao Yicheng.

00:00:35.496 --> 00:00:36.136
I dare you!

00:00:36.992 --> 00:00:38.472
Do you think I dare?

00:00:39.672 --> 00:00:40.352
Stop it!

00:00:40.712 --> 00:00:41.792
You know me.

00:00:41.792 --> 00:00:43.040
I'll do anything.

00:00:44.152 --> 00:00:44.872
You

00:00:44.872 --> 00:00:46.472
are

00:00:46.472 --> 00:00:47.312
shameless.

00:00:48.272 --> 00:00:49.552
I don't care.

00:00:50.592 --> 00:00:51.272
Zhen'er!

00:00:52.552 --> 00:00:53.232
Zhen'er!

00:00:56.224 --> 00:00:57.712
Zhen'er.

00:00:58.552 --> 00:00:59.072
Zhen'er!

00:00:59.072 --> 00:01:00.472
Your Highness, don't barge in!

00:01:03.072 --> 00:01:04.312
Zhen'er isn't here.

00:01:04.592 --> 00:01:05.872
I clearly just heard it.

00:01:06.032 --> 00:01:08.032
Do you wish to marry Lu Zhen'er?

00:01:09.312 --> 00:01:09.992
Yes.

00:01:10.392 --> 00:01:11.512
That can be arranged.

00:01:12.072 --> 00:01:12.672
Fu An!

00:01:13.272 --> 00:01:14.432
Invite Lu Zhen'er over.

00:01:15.472 --> 00:01:16.032
Yes.

00:01:22.912 --> 00:01:23.592
Choose.

00:01:26.472 --> 00:01:27.352
Introduce yourselves.

00:01:27.472 --> 00:01:28.952
I'm Lu Zhen'er No. one.

00:01:28.952 --> 00:01:30.072
I'm Lu Zhen'er No. two.

00:01:30.072 --> 00:01:31.992
- I'm Lu Zhen'er No. three.
- What do you mean?

00:01:31.992 --> 00:01:33.272
- I'm Lu Zhen'er...
- Stop.

00:01:34.232 --> 00:01:35.952
Xiao Wenjing!

00:01:36.312 --> 00:01:38.312
You want to marry Lu Zhen'er.

00:01:38.312 --> 00:01:39.392
Their name is Lu Zhen'er.

00:01:39.392 --> 00:01:40.552
Take whoever pleases you

00:01:40.552 --> 00:01:42.672
to your mansion for the wedding today.

00:01:42.672 --> 00:01:44.312
Xiao Wenjing,

00:01:44.312 --> 00:01:45.272
you dare mock me!

00:01:45.992 --> 00:01:48.432
What gives you such audacity

00:01:48.432 --> 00:01:51.072
to boss me around repeatedly

00:01:51.072 --> 00:01:52.152
and shout disrespectfully?

00:01:52.752 --> 00:01:54.032
By your behavior,

00:01:54.032 --> 00:01:54.784
anyone will think

00:01:55.072 --> 00:01:56.992
you were the late emperor reborn!

00:01:57.432 --> 00:01:59.232
Nonsense! Utterly absurd!

00:01:59.352 --> 00:02:00.512
You're not the late emperor,

00:02:01.392 --> 00:02:03.352
so remember your place.

00:02:07.072 --> 00:02:07.872
Yes.

00:02:09.112 --> 00:02:09.712
Enough.

00:02:10.792 --> 00:02:12.472
Pick a Lu Zhen'er to go with you.

00:02:12.792 --> 00:02:15.632
Keep them for yourself,

00:02:16.432 --> 00:02:17.872
Your Majesty.

00:02:18.712 --> 00:02:19.832
I'll take my leave.

00:02:21.248 --> 00:02:23.712
- If unsatisfied,
- (Xiao Wenjing is utterly shameless,)

00:02:23.712 --> 00:02:25.032
- (resorting to such a trick.)
- I'll select more for you.

00:02:26.272 --> 00:02:27.905
(I give up.)

00:02:29.232 --> 00:02:30.032
Why not eat?

00:02:30.432 --> 00:02:31.312
Let me out!

00:02:31.952 --> 00:02:32.512
No.

00:02:32.512 --> 00:02:33.312
Why?

00:02:33.392 --> 00:02:34.352
It's dangerous outside.

00:02:34.352 --> 00:02:35.752
It's comfortable here.

00:02:35.752 --> 00:02:37.192
Yindan will keep you company.

00:02:37.192 --> 00:02:38.352
Is locking me up fun?

00:02:40.192 --> 00:02:41.192
Of course, it is.

00:02:41.632 --> 00:02:42.672
Don't know your motives.

00:02:47.832 --> 00:02:49.152
I made this myself.

00:02:49.152 --> 00:02:50.072
I sneaked a bite.

00:02:50.072 --> 00:02:50.656
Feed you?

00:02:59.712 --> 00:03:00.952
Want me to pressure you?

00:03:02.552 --> 00:03:03.672
How will you pressure me?

00:03:04.032 --> 00:03:05.552
By threatening Yindan?

00:03:05.552 --> 00:03:06.872
Or the imperial chef's life?

00:03:07.592 --> 00:03:08.160
You said

00:03:08.552 --> 00:03:09.632
you want to go home,

00:03:09.992 --> 00:03:11.312
but can you?

00:03:12.352 --> 00:03:14.232
You relish power
and act without restraint.

00:03:14.712 --> 00:03:16.472
Will you adjust to the modern world's

00:03:16.472 --> 00:03:18.072
rules and constraints?

00:03:22.272 --> 00:03:23.192
Eat it or don't.

00:03:25.952 --> 00:03:26.672
Your Highness!

00:03:26.672 --> 00:03:27.432
Yindan!

00:03:28.632 --> 00:03:29.952
Did he threaten you?

00:03:29.952 --> 00:03:30.472
No.

00:03:30.752 --> 00:03:31.792
Good.

00:03:32.632 --> 00:03:33.592
Your Highness,

00:03:33.592 --> 00:03:35.752
do you wish to marry Prince Rui?

00:03:36.912 --> 00:03:38.392
Marrying him

00:03:38.392 --> 00:03:39.472
means leaving the palace.

00:03:39.472 --> 00:03:41.152
Marriage isn't child's play,

00:03:41.752 --> 00:03:43.472
especially for us women.

00:03:43.472 --> 00:03:44.432
Marry the wrong person

00:03:44.432 --> 00:03:45.712
and your life will be ruined.

00:03:47.072 --> 00:03:49.392
Don't think that way.

00:03:51.792 --> 00:03:52.672
Gender doesn't matter.

00:03:53.232 --> 00:03:55.592
If you're unhappy in marriage,

00:03:55.592 --> 00:03:57.024
be brave to leave anytime.

00:03:57.472 --> 00:03:58.496
And in your life,

00:03:58.592 --> 00:04:00.128
no matter when you start anew,

00:04:01.152 --> 00:04:03.232
you must never wrong yourself.

00:04:12.512 --> 00:04:13.672
This nightgown

00:04:13.672 --> 00:04:15.904
was sewed by my mother

00:04:16.192 --> 00:04:17.824
when I married the late emperor.

00:04:18.992 --> 00:04:20.112
She hoped

00:04:20.112 --> 00:04:22.392
we would be in perfect harmony

00:04:22.392 --> 00:04:23.552
and united as one.

00:04:24.392 --> 00:04:26.672
His Majesty loved me wearing
this nightgown the most.

00:04:26.672 --> 00:04:28.480
- Indeed.
- So many years have passed.

00:04:29.392 --> 00:04:32.192
Your Majesty looks so beautiful in it.

00:04:32.832 --> 00:04:33.592
I'm old now.

00:04:34.112 --> 00:04:36.112
Not at all.

00:04:37.192 --> 00:04:39.192
I'm a mother now,

00:04:39.192 --> 00:04:40.192
so I'm old.

00:04:40.992 --> 00:04:42.632
When my child grows up,

00:04:42.952 --> 00:04:44.992
I'll have become an old woman.

00:04:45.472 --> 00:04:46.712
No.

00:04:46.712 --> 00:04:48.752
When the young prince grows up,

00:04:48.752 --> 00:04:50.392
marries, and has his children,

00:04:50.392 --> 00:04:51.776
Your Majesty will still be young.

00:04:52.112 --> 00:04:54.352
You always know how to cheer me up.

00:04:54.912 --> 00:04:55.832
By the way,

00:04:56.912 --> 00:04:58.552
teach me to make shoes tomorrow.

00:04:59.032 --> 00:05:00.960
I wish to personally make a pair

00:05:01.432 --> 00:05:02.792
of tiger-head shoes for my kid.

00:05:03.792 --> 00:05:06.752
Also, clothes, toys.

00:05:07.072 --> 00:05:07.936
I want

00:05:08.032 --> 00:05:09.672
to make them myself.

00:05:10.312 --> 00:05:11.192
- Your Majesty!
- What's wrong?

00:05:11.872 --> 00:05:12.632
Fire!

00:05:22.272 --> 00:05:23.952
Fire!

00:05:26.552 --> 00:05:28.072
Fire!

00:05:29.232 --> 00:05:30.752
Fire.

00:05:39.312 --> 00:05:40.832
Lu,

00:05:40.832 --> 00:05:42.552
look, I'm also a deer.

00:05:43.312 --> 00:05:43.952
Eat something.

00:05:45.752 --> 00:05:47.072
How can I get you to eat?

00:05:49.112 --> 00:05:50.152
Let me marry Prince Rui.

00:05:50.152 --> 00:05:50.880
Never!

00:05:51.392 --> 00:05:52.352
Let me leave the palace!

00:05:52.952 --> 00:05:53.632
Choose another.

00:05:54.072 --> 00:05:54.752
Xiao Wenjing,

00:05:55.072 --> 00:05:56.096
are you amusing yourself?

00:05:56.592 --> 00:05:57.912
You have beauties in your harem

00:05:58.392 --> 00:05:59.392
and Noble Consort Qing.

00:05:59.712 --> 00:06:01.112
Stop stringing me along!

00:06:01.752 --> 00:06:02.832
What Noble Consort Qing?

00:06:03.792 --> 00:06:06.192
That day when I was ill,

00:06:06.192 --> 00:06:08.232
you were being lovey-dovey with her.

00:06:09.112 --> 00:06:10.032
When were you ill?

00:06:11.592 --> 00:06:12.752
Two days ago!

00:06:12.872 --> 00:06:14.672
Why didn't you send Fu An to me?

00:06:15.312 --> 00:06:16.792
Yindan went with him to you!

00:06:17.272 --> 00:06:18.912
But you focus on Noble Consort Qing!

00:06:26.152 --> 00:06:27.632
What are you grinning about?

00:06:27.792 --> 00:06:29.312
I am simply overjoyed.

00:06:30.512 --> 00:06:31.392
Be quiet.

00:06:32.672 --> 00:06:33.472
Yes.

00:06:39.832 --> 00:06:41.552
I didn't know you were ill that day.

00:06:41.552 --> 00:06:43.632
Nothing happened between us.

00:06:44.712 --> 00:06:45.472
Never mind.

00:06:45.472 --> 00:06:46.432
None of that matters.

00:06:46.792 --> 00:06:47.472
I would

00:06:47.472 --> 00:06:49.752
never fall for an ancient person!

00:06:53.312 --> 00:06:55.072
Then you like me?

00:07:00.552 --> 00:07:01.872
Nonsense!

00:07:02.952 --> 00:07:04.232
Why don't you let me go?

00:07:05.992 --> 00:07:08.312
Because I must watch you

00:07:09.752 --> 00:07:12.232
at all times closely to prevent you

00:07:12.232 --> 00:07:13.512
from suddenly killing me.

00:07:13.872 --> 00:07:14.872
Is that so?

00:07:15.632 --> 00:07:16.752
Of course.

00:07:17.712 --> 00:07:18.432
Why imprison me

00:07:18.432 --> 00:07:19.952
in your chamber?

00:07:19.952 --> 00:07:21.392
Throw me straight into the jail.

00:07:21.672 --> 00:07:22.912
Take the hint,

00:07:22.912 --> 00:07:24.432
or suffer the consequences!

00:07:24.432 --> 00:07:25.552
The consequences.

00:07:28.992 --> 00:07:29.872
Suit yourself.

00:07:29.872 --> 00:07:30.952
Starve for all I care!

00:07:46.872 --> 00:07:47.952
What are you doing?

00:07:47.952 --> 00:07:49.072
Are you insane?

00:07:50.712 --> 00:07:52.512
Your Majesty! Trouble!

00:07:52.512 --> 00:07:54.752
Something happened to Her Majesty.

00:07:58.712 --> 00:07:59.672
What happened?

00:07:59.672 --> 00:08:00.872
She caught fire.

00:08:01.192 --> 00:08:01.992
What?

00:08:02.112 --> 00:08:04.072
Her Majesty caught fire!

00:08:06.512 --> 00:08:07.632
- Spontaneous human combustion!
- Spontaneous human combustion!

00:08:07.992 --> 00:08:10.512
They said she suddenly caught fire!

00:08:11.032 --> 00:08:11.832
Is she dead?

00:08:11.952 --> 00:08:12.712
No.

00:08:12.712 --> 00:08:14.432
Physician Wang is treating her.

00:08:16.232 --> 00:08:17.056
White phosphorus.

00:08:18.992 --> 00:08:21.752
Your Highness, what is white phosphorus?

00:08:21.912 --> 00:08:23.192
White phosphorus is flammable.

00:08:23.192 --> 00:08:24.792
The heat from clothing friction

00:08:24.792 --> 00:08:26.032
can ignite it.

00:08:26.272 --> 00:08:27.672
But how do you know this?

00:08:29.232 --> 00:08:30.432
She read it in a book.

00:08:32.800 --> 00:08:33.820
Hmm.

00:08:37.552 --> 00:08:38.992
My child...

00:08:38.992 --> 00:08:40.712
How is my child?

00:08:43.592 --> 00:08:44.512
Say something!

00:08:45.912 --> 00:08:46.872
I...

00:08:46.872 --> 00:08:47.752
I dare not say.

00:08:48.192 --> 00:08:49.472
Speak!

00:08:49.472 --> 00:08:50.912
I'll absolve you of guilt.

00:08:52.552 --> 00:08:54.592
Your Majesty was never pregnant.

00:08:54.592 --> 00:08:56.192
Nonsense!

00:08:56.192 --> 00:08:58.072
Clearly, my belly

00:08:58.072 --> 00:08:59.632
growing bigger each day.

00:09:00.032 --> 00:09:01.832
How could I not be pregnant?

00:09:03.152 --> 00:09:06.992
- No signs of pregnancy, but...
- Nonsense!

00:09:06.992 --> 00:09:07.992
Utter nonsense!

00:09:07.992 --> 00:09:10.032
Guards! Drag him out!

00:09:10.032 --> 00:09:10.792
Beat him to death.

00:09:10.792 --> 00:09:12.312
Please spare me!

00:09:12.312 --> 00:09:14.392
Please spare me!

00:09:14.392 --> 00:09:16.232
Show mercy.

00:09:16.352 --> 00:09:17.888
I must be pregnant!

00:09:18.752 --> 00:09:20.592
How could I not be pregnant?

00:09:22.392 --> 00:09:23.752
Your Majesty,

00:09:23.752 --> 00:09:25.408
Physician Wang is highly skilled.

00:09:25.992 --> 00:09:26.944
He shouldn't

00:09:27.352 --> 00:09:28.472
have misdiagnosed.

00:09:29.112 --> 00:09:30.720
Where did my child go?

00:09:31.632 --> 00:09:33.552
Someone must've cursed me

00:09:33.552 --> 00:09:35.192
and stole my child!

00:09:39.032 --> 00:09:40.544
I'll go to Master Wu.

00:09:41.112 --> 00:09:42.592
He'll surely have a solution.

00:09:43.232 --> 00:09:44.752
Your Majesty, watch your step.

00:09:53.592 --> 00:09:54.392
Your Highness.

00:09:57.432 --> 00:09:58.720
Stop sighing.

00:09:59.192 --> 00:10:00.992
Sighing harms your health.

00:10:03.552 --> 00:10:04.472
Understood.

00:10:05.472 --> 00:10:08.352
How do you regard His Majesty now?

00:10:10.392 --> 00:10:12.352
Still wish to be his consort?

00:10:13.032 --> 00:10:13.832
No.

00:10:14.592 --> 00:10:16.992
If you marry Prince Rui,

00:10:17.552 --> 00:10:18.672
would you truly be happy?

00:10:20.672 --> 00:10:21.632
Yindan,

00:10:21.632 --> 00:10:22.952
why do you ask?

00:10:23.392 --> 00:10:26.552
I wish for your happiness.

00:10:28.832 --> 00:10:30.232
As long as you're by my side,

00:10:30.232 --> 00:10:31.200
I'll be happy.

00:10:35.872 --> 00:10:37.272
Come with us.

00:10:37.272 --> 00:10:38.192
Who are you?

00:10:38.192 --> 00:10:39.952
- What are you doing?
- Your Highness!

00:10:49.760 --> 00:10:50.712
Chen Wanyi,

00:10:51.312 --> 00:10:52.552
why arrest me again?

00:10:58.848 --> 00:11:00.512
Your Majesty, what are you doing?

00:11:01.232 --> 00:11:02.312
Lu Zhen'er,

00:11:03.192 --> 00:11:05.272
please save my child!

00:11:06.072 --> 00:11:07.472
What child?

00:11:07.472 --> 00:11:09.312
I said you weren't pregnant.

00:11:09.432 --> 00:11:11.832
No, I had a child!

00:11:11.832 --> 00:11:13.792
I could feel he is there.

00:11:13.792 --> 00:11:14.792
Lu Zhen'er,

00:11:14.992 --> 00:11:16.232
if only you forgive me...

00:11:16.232 --> 00:11:16.872
And Yindan.

00:11:16.872 --> 00:11:18.232
If you'd both forgive me,

00:11:18.232 --> 00:11:19.552
write me a letter of pardon

00:11:19.792 --> 00:11:20.672
to cleanse my karma,

00:11:20.672 --> 00:11:22.432
my child will return!

00:11:23.192 --> 00:11:24.512
I don't understand.

00:11:24.992 --> 00:11:26.352
Master Wu said

00:11:27.072 --> 00:11:28.952
my accumulated negative karma

00:11:28.952 --> 00:11:30.400
made my child vanish.

00:11:32.592 --> 00:11:33.992
If you forgive me...

00:11:34.392 --> 00:11:35.152
Lu Zhen'er,

00:11:36.232 --> 00:11:37.432
if only you forgive me,

00:11:37.752 --> 00:11:39.352
I'll do anything you ask.

00:11:40.032 --> 00:11:40.912
Chen Wanyi,

00:11:41.272 --> 00:11:42.992
no ghosts or gods in this world.

00:11:43.272 --> 00:11:45.792
- You never even had...
- Yes, I did!

00:11:45.792 --> 00:11:47.552
I did have a child!

00:11:48.992 --> 00:11:50.232
Lu Zhen'er,

00:11:50.392 --> 00:11:51.512
forgive me!

00:11:51.512 --> 00:11:53.632
It was my first child
with the late emperor.

00:11:54.152 --> 00:11:55.592
Help me!

00:11:58.712 --> 00:11:59.552
But...

00:11:59.552 --> 00:12:00.232
Your Highness,

00:12:01.552 --> 00:12:02.432
write it for her.

00:12:03.632 --> 00:12:04.752
Consider it

00:12:05.512 --> 00:12:06.672
pity for a mother.

00:12:29.211 --> 00:12:32.355
(Settling the score with Chen Wanyi,
by Lu Zhen'er)

00:12:36.272 --> 00:12:38.152
Thank you both!

00:12:40.712 --> 00:12:41.432
Yindan,

00:12:42.272 --> 00:12:43.272
I'm sorry.

00:12:43.272 --> 00:12:44.512
No need, Your Majesty.

00:12:44.992 --> 00:12:45.992
Not doing this for you.

00:12:46.912 --> 00:12:48.592
Mothers endure enough hardship.

00:12:53.512 --> 00:12:55.112
My child is saved!

00:12:55.112 --> 00:12:56.672
My child is saved!

00:13:01.472 --> 00:13:02.992
She's ill,

00:13:02.992 --> 00:13:04.392
not pregnant.

00:13:04.752 --> 00:13:05.992
Yet she

00:13:05.992 --> 00:13:07.752
believes she became a mother.

00:13:07.872 --> 00:13:11.552
Pitiable, yet not blameless.

00:13:13.272 --> 00:13:14.472
Yindan,

00:13:14.472 --> 00:13:16.072
were you thinking of you mother?

00:13:17.712 --> 00:13:19.512
My mother

00:13:19.512 --> 00:13:21.312
was very nice to me.

00:13:21.672 --> 00:13:22.592
She...

00:13:23.752 --> 00:13:24.552
She

00:13:25.112 --> 00:13:26.192
passed away

00:13:27.712 --> 00:13:29.232
to protect me.

00:13:31.432 --> 00:13:32.632
Don't worry.

00:13:32.632 --> 00:13:34.792
In the future, I'll protect you.

00:13:49.472 --> 00:13:50.872
Amitabha.

00:13:50.872 --> 00:13:53.072
Bless my child.

00:13:53.072 --> 00:13:54.832
Amitabha.

00:13:54.832 --> 00:13:55.672
Your Majesty.

00:13:56.432 --> 00:13:57.872
What can I do for you?

00:13:59.072 --> 00:14:00.112
Yicheng,

00:14:00.312 --> 00:14:02.152
our child is gone.

00:14:04.592 --> 00:14:05.696
What happened to your face?

00:14:06.632 --> 00:14:08.312
I said our child is gone!

00:14:09.472 --> 00:14:10.272
That's for the best.

00:14:11.032 --> 00:14:12.152
Yicheng,

00:14:12.952 --> 00:14:14.792
that was your child!

00:14:14.792 --> 00:14:16.512
Your flesh and blood!

00:14:17.432 --> 00:14:18.312
Preposterous!

00:14:19.432 --> 00:14:22.032
Do you not believe that child was yours?

00:14:22.392 --> 00:14:23.992
Besides the late emperor,

00:14:23.992 --> 00:14:25.712
I have ever had you as a man.

00:14:25.952 --> 00:14:27.272
Who knew that?

